Class CLRCodedIndexField

  • java.lang.Object

    public class CLRCodedIndexField
extends CLRField
implements NIndexable, scala.Product, scala.Serializable
    Field contains a coded token. As such it is an index into to row of a specific table. param: codedTokenIndex param: sfield
